fc227a240f7d1b981ebf3","tid":1778604,"uid":249263,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-11T05:49:09.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">美加議員講對華政策，<br />\n響task2 急要人</span></span><br />\n適逢人權日，世界上人權被打壓嘅國家或地區唔少，當然其中一個亮點係打壓緊香港同新疆嘅中國！<br />\n<br />\n多國政要發推文關注中國打壓人權嘅情況，精選推文遍布task 1 &amp; 2，大家快啲去回應啦！<br />\n<br />\n記得落hashtag #humanrights #HumanRightsDay 呀～<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\">出門之前 rt like reply</span><br />\nTwitter組24小時keep住更新<br />\n幫手retweet<br />\n㩒入👉<a href=\"https://t.me/TwitterHelpBot\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2FTwitterHelpBot&d=doP1hY1jTMShcZ7HAjrDwnhUmc0vP2awQoWdJLgJf%2FY%3D&h=9911f8b7\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/TwitterHelpBot</a><br />\n然後打 /task 攞任務"}]}